  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK395">
<l>uṭaiyārmu ṉillārpō lēkkaṟṟuṅ kaṟṟār</l>
<l>kaṭaiyarē kallā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The unlearned are inferior to the learned, before whom they stand begging, as the destitute before the wealthy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
